Custom pipes:
    to convert names to capitalize format
    suPeRMaN iS On thE mOOn, false -> Superman is on the moon 
    suPeRMaN iS On thE mOOn, true -> Superman Is On The Moon 

    to find power of a num
    4, 3 -> 4*4*4
    5, 2 -> 5*5

    @Pipe({
        name: "capitalize"
    })
    class CapitalizePipe{
        transform(arg1, arg2=false){
            return new value;
        }
    }